    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty. It\u2019s honestly in such amazing shape, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014always garage-kept and pampered. It\u2019s basically flawless and drives like a dream. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \ud83d\ude0a",
