    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly investment-grade vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint retains its deep, glass-like factory luster, protected by a professional ceramic coating with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Every panel gap is laser-straight, and the wheels are free of any curb rash or pitting. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather seats remain firm and free of any bolster wear or creasing, and the original protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. It still retains that distinct 'new car' scent. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive binder of every service record from day one, performed exclusively at certified dealerships. The engine bay is immaculate, the undercarriage is spotless, and the tires are high-performance Michelins with over 90% tread remaining. This isn't just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning collector who demands perfection in every detail.",
      "price": 44500.0,
