      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, reflects a standard of care rarely seen in the secondary market. Mechanically impeccable and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this unit is an exemplary acquisition for the sophisticated driver who demands excellence without compromise.",
