    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in truly incredible, like-new condition\u2014seriously, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like a dream. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. I'd love for you to come by and see it for yourself; you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
