    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the zenith of the S54 inline-six platform. The 3.2L powerplant features a forged steel crankshaft and graphite-coated pistons, delivering a linear power band to a stratospheric 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen boasts a documented reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, addressing the chassis's critical reciprocating stress points. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides precise tactile engagement, paired with a variable M-differential lock for optimal torque distribution during lateral acceleration. The exterior retains its factory paint depth and luster, with zero evidence of panel gap deviation or underbody oxidation. A museum-quality specimen for the technical purist.",
